title: Nero Portable 16 0 24 0 Multilingual .Portable Full
description:
What's New in Nero Burning ROM 2015?

Nero AirBurn: Burn files straight from your Android & iOS device
New Nero Launcher with instant access to tasks and tutorials
New Manual app to help you learn and master Nero Burning ROM 2015


Extract and run NeroPortable or NeroExpressPortable.
To change language edit NeroPortable.ini with Language=xx-XX (cs-CZ, da-DK, de-DE, el-GR, en-US, es-ES, fi-FI, fr-FR, hu-HU, it-IT, ja-JP, ko-KR, nb-NO, nl-NL, pl-PL, pt-BR, pt-PT, ru-RU, sv-SE, th-TH, tr-TR, zh-CN, zh-TW) and delete Data folder before restarting.
Settings of installed Nero should be preserved
